---
// ヒーロー右側の自作ビジュアル（浮遊カード構成）
---

<div class="art" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="card-f c1">
    <div class="bar"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
    <div class="code"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
    <div class="glow"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card-f c2">
    <div class="ico">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path d="M7 18a4 4 0 0 1 .4-8 5.5 5.5 0 0 1 10.6 1.3A3.6 3.6 0 0 1 17.5 18z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h4>クラウド構築</h4>
    <p>設計から運用まで一貫支援</p>
  </div>

  <div class="badge">
    <svg class="drop" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
      <path d="M32 8c10 13 16 21 16 29a16 16 0 0 1-32 0c0-8 6-16 16-29z" fill="#2A86C0"/>
      <path d="M42 14c6-3 13-2 13-2s.6 7-3.6 11-9.4 3-9.4 3 .6-8 0-12z" fill="#98C727"/>
    </svg>
    <div><b>OiS</b><small>潤いを、技術で。</small></div>
  </div>

  <span class="float-dot d1"></span>
  <span class="float-dot d2"></span>
</div>

<style>
  .art {
    position: relative;
    height: 460px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .card-f {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 22px;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
  }
  .c1 {
    inset: 18px 50px 92px 0;
    background: var(--grad);
    overflow: hidden;
    animation: floaty 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .c1 .bar {
    position: absolute;
    left: 18px;
    right: 18px;
    height: 34px;
    top: 18px;
    border-radius: 14px 14px 0 0;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 0 14px;
  }
  .c1 .bar span {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }
  .code {
    position: absolute;
    left: 34px;
    right: 34px;
    top: 78px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .code i {
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    display: block;
  }
  .code i:nth-child(1) { width: 62%; }
  .code i:nth-child(2) { width: 84%; }
  .code i:nth-child(3) { width: 48%; }
  .code i:nth-child(4) { width: 72%; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); }
  .code i:nth-child(5) { width: 40%; }
  .c1 .glow {
    position: absolute;
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    right: -40px;
    bottom: -40px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), transparent 65%);
  }
  .c2 {
    width: 215px;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 30px;
    padding: 18px;
    animation: floaty 7s ease-in-out infinite 0.8s;
  }
  .c2 .ico {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--blue-soft);
    color: var(--blue);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .c2 h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .c2 p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 4px 0 0; }
  .badge {
    position: absolute;
    left: 4px;
    bottom: 18px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    animation: floaty 6s ease-in-out infinite 0.4s;
  }
  .badge .drop { width: 40px; height: 40px; }
  .badge b { font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .badge small { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.72rem; }

  .float-dot {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .d1 {
    width: 14px; height: 14px; background: var(--green);
    top: 6px; right: 30px; box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(152, 199, 39, 0.18);
    animation: floaty 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .d2 {
    width: 10px; height: 10px; background: var(--blue);
    bottom: 80px; left: -6px; box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(42, 134, 192, 0.16);
    animation: floaty 6.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.6s;
  }

  @keyframes floaty {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .c1, .c2, .badge, .float-dot { animation: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .art { height: 380px; max-width: 460px; margin-inline: auto; }
  }
</style>
